parameters:
Ores likely excavated from the mines. Restraints that were
probably used on the workers, and the remains of those who
'didn't make it' here...
It seems there is no lie in what's been brought here.

...A teleportation circle? Such an advanced magical device,
there's no way mere scoundrels could prepare this.

The stones and workers carried from the mines are likely
taken further ahead...
There's no sign of people, huh...
